download url "MAY 2013" WordPress Codex "Function Reference"
============================================================

NAME
----

download url - Downloads a url to a local temporary file using the WordPress HTTP

SYNOPSIS
--------

Downloads a url to a local temporary file using the WordPress HTTP
Class. Please note that the calling function must unlink() the file.

PARAMETERS
----------

 `$url` 
:   ([*string*](/How_to_Pass_Tag_Parameters#String "How to Pass Tag Parameters"))
    (*required*) the URL of the file to download
    Default: *None*

 `$timeout` 
:   ([*integer*](/How_to_Pass_Tag_Parameters#Integer "How to Pass Tag Parameters"))
    (*optional*) The timeout for the request to download the file
    default 300 seconds
    Default: 300

RETURN VALUES
-------------

 `` `(mixed)`{style="color:gray"} 
:   WP\_Error on failure, string Filename on success.

CHANGE LOG
----------

Since: [2.5](/Version_2.5 "Version 2.5")

SOURCE FILE
-----------

download\_url() is located in `wp-admin/includes/file.php`

